docs.lead_paragraph: LEAD: ''Nova'' presents a story with a happy ending tonight: three young whales go home. Viewers may not be moved to cheers or tears, although certainly they will be pleased. The program, ''Whale Rescue,'' on Channel 13 at 9 o'clock tonight, is about a narrow escape.

headline.main: Review/Television; 'Whale Rescue,' Escape And a Happy Ending
